spec_data.Name: perl-Crypt-SmbHash
spec_data.Description:
This module generates Lanman and NT MD4 style password hashes, using perl-only
code for portability. The module aids in the administration of Samba style
systems.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 09:55:53 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Pure-perl Lanman and NT MD4 hash functions
